data.eml:eml: Carabidae of the European North-East of Russia

This is Occurrence Dataset of the ground beetles in the European North-East of Russia. It consists of data of 225 species, 43 genus, 23 tribas and 2 subfamilies of Carabidae.The basis for these studies was the long-term fees conducted from 1977 to 2015 in the Republic of Komi and the Nenets Autonomous district
